  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nFrom discord (@stefa2k):\r\n\r\nQ: Hi, I'm getting keystoresDir /opt/app/.local/share/lodestar/mainnet/keystores does not exist but I set keystoresDir: /opt/app/keystores in the config yaml via --paramsFile /opt/app/validator.yaml\r\nAm I missing something?\r\n\r\nA: it looks the paramsFile only supports the testnet/mainnet params (the ones from the eth2 spec)\r\nour beacon node lets you override all of the cli options via a file --configFile but it doesn't look like the validator supports that\r\nWe should add the same thing to the validator, but for now, you'd have to add --keystoresDir via cli\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nAllow for validator cli options to be specified in a file, like is possible for the beacon node\r\n",
